snippet.title: Airspace Defender - Launch Date Reveal | Meta Quest Mixed Reality Gameplay
snippet.description:
Airspace Defender is a 3D tabletop arcade game in mixed reality. Manage your city's defenses and thwart enemy attacks with carefully timed retaliatory strikes!
